
# Steam Deck CAC Quick Reference

## Install Middleware

```bash
sudo pacman -S pcsclite ccid opensc firefox
```

## Start CAC Services

```bash
sudo systemctl enable pcscd
sudo systemctl start pcscd
```

## Detect Reader

```bash
pcsc_scan
```

## List CAC Certificates

```bash
pkcs11-tool --module /usr/lib/pkcs11/opensc-pkcs11.so -L
```

## Restart Smart Card Service

```bash
sudo systemctl restart pcscd
```

## Restart Firefox

```bash
pkill firefox
firefox
```
